Data Table Widget

The data table widget (DTW) allows you to view (in a table or list) selected information for multiple objects.

 

Note: To see how to insert and configure the widget look 

To view the filter option select option. You can filter the data presented in the Data table for each of the columns displayed.

 

To sort the result presented in Data table widget use option. If a column displays relationship to more than one system object, there is no sort option.

To create new item of the types presented in the data table widget use .
